MezTal.com Website Audit and Strategic Development Outline (Sandbox Environment)I. Project Scope and Initial Assessment
Initial Request: Assess and improve the new MezTal.com site (Wix Studio editor sandbox) using an SEO guide, create missing pillar pages, and align with a visual sitemap.
Key Initial Task: Identify and address blank/placeholder pages.
II. Current Site Structure and SEO Gaps (Audit Findings)
